snippet.title: BONE APPETIT - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Coming May 8th, 2020! Wishlist it today!
https://store.steampowered.com/app/1256520

When the king steals all the food, whatcha' gonna' do? Raise a skeleton slave to steal it back for you, of course!

From the maker of Hasslevania and Equin: The Lantern comes Bone Appetit- A brand new old-school Metroidvania designed by an authentic old guy!
